        <item>
            <title>2.10.0</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 15:15:29 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>75</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.10.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Features
- **Cmd+Ctrl+1..9**: Load the N-th visible sidebar session into the currently focused pane — no mouse needed.
- **Cmd+Shift+[** and **Cmd+Shift+]**: Cycle the focused pane's session to the previous / next visible open session (sessions already open in another pane are skipped, so cycling stays within the focused pane).

### Changes
- **Cmd+1..9 now focuses the N-th pane** (previously switched to the N-th sidebar session). Focus jumps AND keyboard first-responder moves to that pane's chat input, so typing lands immediately without an extra click.
- Closing a pane now hands keyboard focus to the surviving pane, so \`Cmd+W\` followed by typing just works.

### Bug Fixes
- Fixed the per-model usage row (e.g. Weekly Fable) in the sidebar occasionally flickering on and off. Anthropic's usage endpoint intermittently omits the \`model_scoped\` field from otherwise valid responses; Canopy now keeps the previous value instead of clearing the row when the field is absent.
]]></description>
